---- Navigation ----
Ctrl-h:     Hop to char
K / J:      Jump 10 lines up / down
H / L:      Line start / end

---- Code -----
gd          Go to definition
gr          Go to references
gi          Go to implementation
go          Show hover documentation
(signature help auto-triggers on ( and ,)

Aerial (symbol outline)
<leader>a:  Focus aerial (open if needed)
Ctrl-j:     Next symbol
Ctrl-k:     Previous symbol

---- Buffer Management ----
Ctrl-x:     Close buffer
t / T:      Next / previous buffer
gh/j/k/l:   Move to split (left/down/up/right)
Alt-C-h/j/k/l: Resize splits

---- Search ----
Ctrl-f:     Fuzzy search in current buffer
Ctrl-b:     Find existing buffers
<leader>ff: Find files           <leader>fg: Live grep
<leader>fs: Grep string          <leader>fr: Recent files
<leader>fd: Diagnostics          <leader>fe: Resume last
<leader>ft: Git files            <leader>fb: Buffers
<leader>fl: Reveal current file in Neo-tree

:%s/foo/bar/g   replace all in whole file
:%s/foo/bar/gc  replace all with confirmation
-> ctrl-r+" pastes current register

---- Treesitter incremental selection ----
gnn / grn:  Init / grow selection
grc:        Grow to scope
grm:        Shrink selection

---- Macros ----
qx:         Start recording macro on x
q:          Stop recording
@x / @@:    Run macro x / last run
